data.description: Stunning island home with views of the 13th hole Wild Dunes Resort Harbor Golf Course!    Located on a large corner lot just minutes to the beach and marina.  Huge wrap around porch perfect for grilling, gatherings or a peaceful retreat.  The gourmet kitchen contains dual sub zero refrigerator, six burner gas cooktop and dual ovens.  Eclectic unique dining area with views of the golf course.  The living room sports a gorgeous Italian marble vent less gas fireplace, ship lapped lined walls and Brazilian cherry hardwood floors.  Spacious 1st floor master suite with 2 walk in closets, large jacuzzi tub and separate shower.  The remaining 3 bedrooms are all located on the 2nd floor each have their own ensuite baths.  Two of the bedrooms have an attached additional room which is used as playrooms.   Additional upgrades: 2 new AC units, tankless water heater, new separate ice machine in kitchen as well as new dishwasher. No regime or HOA fees.
